To install:

1) Check you have the following installed:
   - POE (libpoe-perl package under GNU/Debian)
   - Socker (part of the standard Perl distribution)
2) Make sure interject.pl is executable (chmod u+s
   interject.pl)

For each Interject module, to install:

1) cd <module name>
2) perl Makefile.PL
3) make
4) make install

The latest version of Interject can always be found at <http://www.interject.pl/>.
